original_title: Bootsy Collins & His New Rubber Band: Live at Jazz Baltica
overview: Bootsy Collins and his New Rubber Band live at Jazz Baltica, Salzau Germany, 1998, featuring P-Funk legends Garry Shider, Fred Wesley, Rick Gardner, Gary "Mudbone" Cooper and Frankie "Kash" Waddy.
title: Bootsy Collins & His New Rubber Band: Live at Jazz Baltica
